{"tid":1722564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Hi 阿sir","createTime":"2019-11-15T02:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T03:13:08.000Z","uid":192769,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30a7358793f87e096da0fcb6bb1d64d927800cee","tid":1722564,"uid":192769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:33:24.000Z","msg":"有理由相信popo已變陣。不再強攻，而打分化，鬼滲透，文宣<br />\n<br />\n中大圍城、封路、撤走內地生，國際生後，一直未攻；相反大量疑似鬼post 鬼comment 鬼行為出現<br />\n<br />\n拆解方法：<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">無時無刻防範周圍既係鬼。</span></strong><br />\n發夢黎講，先唔好講，好多時你見到既人都係第一次見；再者即使見左幾次都可以係臥底埋伏。唔係要捉鬼，而係要保護自己，同保護場運動。唔好比佢拎到你既資料，唔好因為佢地既某d 行為而影響你對場運動既熱誠。唔需要確定對方係咪鬼，即係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔使捉鬼</strong></span>，因為點都捉唔曬，自己心入面打個底，獨立思考就ok.<br />\n<br />\n鬼posts, comments 黎講，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>當你認為係鬼/分化；不推文加句'hi, 阿sir' 即可</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb1c83d8d397e05d516e0c9ff1092192b4c8136","tid":1722564,"uid":192769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:33:44.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"8466f406c96581a8c00ebdc8107f10bc874d0738","tid":1722564,"uid":192769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:33:54.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"7a2e254997c065c624e8aafd2221da392b53a1eb","tid":1722564,"uid":192769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:34:05.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"296a3ba61af720ad5149baa59b7583daf45d0e86","tid":1722564,"uid":192769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:34:15.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"cc5d40819ae54874ffb3d0e395c1215dcf3b6bb7","tid":1722564,"uid":192769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:34:25.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"b6a514f14b427c6bb10ef64ab6acfafbabf02358","tid":1722564,"uid":192769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime